{"tid":2262564,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"男子被指去年襲擊民建聯成員吳奮金及破壞其街站 唐偉倫裁定罪成 還押候判","createTime":"2020-10-29T08:08:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T10:59:51.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"254d3bd9951b76fec0c905bf81d0296a04783260","tid":2262564,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T08:08:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/10783\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F10783&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5Kit%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=e7b7242d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/10783</a><br />\n<br />\n#九龍城裁判法院第八庭<br />\n#唐偉倫暫委裁判官<br />\n#1021何文田<br />\n#裁決<br />\n<br />\n李 (31)<br />\n<br />\n已認罪：<br />\n控罪一，三，四：刑事損壞<br />\n‼️罪名成立‼️<br />\n<br />\n不認罪：<br />\n控罪二：抗拒警務人員<br />\n‼️罪名成立‼️<br />\n控罪五：普通襲擊<br />\n‼️罪名成立‼️<br />\n控罪六：刑事恐嚇<br />\n❌罪名不成立❌<br />\n<br />\n押後至11月12日1130九龍城裁判法院第十二庭判刑，索取背景報告，期間還押‼️<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">被告大聲向裁判官哭訴，並沒有襲擊過吳奮金‼️</span></strong>"},{"pid":"2a5e112a3b9887b941bfbe23045816e293e6b6aa","tid":2262564,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T08:14:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0cab3f222beb056b2bf9b9259b2836730e80497","tid":2262564,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a5e112a3b9887b941bfbe23045816e293e6b6aa","tid":2262564,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T08:14:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T08:15:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/n